content:
Shit its true the eurprates river dried up it must have been released...
She honesty would make a great horror movie villian. Think a little female freddy kruger mixed in with crypt kepper and nemesis from resisdent evil... she crawled out of 9th circle of Hell.... is thier a exosists in the comment section... i feel like i am looking at someone who is stuck between our world and the next...
She was like a virgin when the dead sea was sick....
Her face has so many wrinkles it could hold a 8 day rain...
How did she survive noah flood
Who found the door in ghostbusters cartoon saying dont open till doomsday and decided to jump the gun....
What lab did this escape from...
Is this extra dimensional...
Is this where covid came from. Hope she closes those legs before we have another pandemic...
